Fit Standardized Simple Mediation Model for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution - Structural Equation Modeling (Single Task)

Source: R/mvn_complete_std_fit.sem.R
mvn_std_fit.sem_task.Rd

Fit Standardized Simple Mediation Model for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution - Structural Equation Modeling (Single Task)

mvn_std_fit.sem_task(taskid, dir = getwd(), overwrite = FALSE)

Arguments

taskid

Numeric. Task ID.
dir

Character string. Directory where results of mvn_dat_* are stored.
overwrite

Logical. Overwrite existing results.
